These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, taxi, bike
City: new-york, edinburgh, venice
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the taxi##2
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Transport      | taxi | bike | boat |
| City   | edinburgh     | new-york    | venice   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, snowboarding
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, mauve, ivory
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes apricot and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Sport   | cycling    | snowboarding        | surfing |
| Color     | mauve | ivory | apricot         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blue, purple
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian, argentine
1. the canadian is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is between the nigerian and the person who likes purple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Color   | blue | fuchsia     | purple |
| Nationality        | nigerian  | argentine | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, december
House: futuristic, townhouse, cape-cod
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the futuristic house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the townhouse house and the futuristic house##2
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Birthday   | october  | december     | july |
| House           | townhouse | cape-cod | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bluemaster, dunhill
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, swimming
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | dunhill     | swisher |
| Sport     | swimming    | golf | weightlifting    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
House: gothic-revival, modern, art-deco
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, bridge
1. the person playing chess is between the art-deco house and the gothic-revival house##2
2. the gothic-revival house is the person playing snooker##1
3. the modern house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| House   | gothic-revival  | modern   | art-deco        |
| Game         | snooker | chess | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, dahlia
3 different pets are kept: rat, frog, horse
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person who growsdahlia and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Flower          | daffodil  | balloon-flower  | dahlia |
| Pet   | frog | rat | horse     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, vegafina, fonseca
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, lemon, zucchini
1. the vegafina-smoker is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating lemon is between the vegafina-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | cain  | vegafina  |
| Food   | cranberry | lemon | zucchini |

