.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, electronic, salsa
City: san-francisco, venice, boston
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan electronic##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the fan salsa and the person traveling to venice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre       | salsa | country | electronic  |
| City   | boston    | san-francisco        | venice |

