2. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Sport         | sailing | skiing | rowing |
| Beverage   | lemonade     | tea    | juice |

