.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, blend, davidoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, blue, fuchsia
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the person who likes blue##2
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Cigar      | davidoff | blend   | pall-mall |
| Color   | fuchsia  | purple | blue   |

 